reviewText: From the back of the box (Video Gems edition): "The beautiful rainbow trout. The mighty fighting albacore. The majestic sea bass. They're just a few of the catches you'll make when you accompany the inimitable Gadabout Gaddis as he goes FISHING U.S.A...Follow America's 'Flying Fisherman' on a cross-country tour of the vanishing wilderness. Any angling nature lover will welcome it - hook, line and sinker!"
